        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
This is not my idea, but I thought I'd throw it out there for you all to discuss. It was posted on the Caster's Realms forums, and I'm curious what you think.

<BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>
I personally would love it if necromancers could cast feign death on someone else. 
Scene: Any high level raid where wipeout in progress...

Raid_Leader_01 /shouts "Feign the clerics!"

Necromancers proceed to cast Feign Death on the clerics who then /q to safety...

Talk about increased raid desirability for necromancers...hehe 

--------------------

Zarros, High Elven Cleric of Tunare
Saryrn Server 

