        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> It occurs to me that it might be kinda appropriate if a positive modifier for the FD role were applied when you're in Skeletal/Spectre form.  It seems that the illusion would be more complete and thus more likely to succeed.</P><P>The balancing side of this, would be that you're still losing HPs.  With everything but Call of Bones, this HP loss is pretty significant.  When the illusion is removed you'd have a chance to lose the FD.</P><P>Dunno how difficult this'd be to code and it seems unlikely to happen, but it's just a thought.</P><P>AlAaraaf.</P><P><BR> </font></td>
