id then its just a matter of coincidence right.  And if there were 10 necros do you think there is any raid leader who woudlnt want to swap 9 of those necros for other classes.</P><P>As far as the EE's go, its never going to be removed, nor should it, we arent clerics.  Just because you fd a cleric or 2 doesnt mean you or another necro on the raid cant get out either, after feigning clerics harmshield then run out of AE and feign yourself, whats so hard about that.  And frankly I'd rather die and be res'd in 2 mins later than have to use an EE, plus clerics have the advantage of being able to click people in with no mana at all and get a raid force up much quicker than a necro can.</P><P>These are the kind of usefeul unique abilities we need.</P><P> </font></td>
